description: In 2028 Detroit, when Alex Murphy, a loving husband, father and good cop, is critically injured in the line of duty, the multinational conglomerate OmniCorp sees their chance for a part-man, part-robot police officer.

description: After a violent incident with a special chemical, a research scientist is turned into a swamp plant monster.

title: TRON
description: A computer hacker is abducted into the digital world and forced to participate in gladiatorial games where his only chance of escape is with the help of a heroic security program.

title: Super

title: The Rocketeer

title: The Old Guard 2
description: Plot Unknown. Sequel to The Old Guard (2020).

description: After being hypnotized by his sister-in-law, a man begins seeing haunting visions of a girl's ghost and a mystery begins to unfold around him.

description: The comic "Bluntman and Chronic" is based on real-life stoners Jay and Silent Bob, so when they get no profit from a big-screen adaptation, they set out to wreck the movie.

title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem
description: CG-animated feature film based on the superhero team

title: Barb Wire
description: During the Second American Civil War in 2017, Barb Wire owns a nightclub called the Hammerhead. Things become complicated when her ex-lover Axel Hood, who is married to the fugitive Corrina Devonshire, re-enters her life.

title: Disaster Movie
description: Over the course of one evening, an unsuspecting group of twenty-somethings find themselves bombarded by a series of natural disasters and catastrophic events.

title: Howard the Duck
description: A sarcastic humanoid duck is pulled from his homeworld to Earth where he must stop an alien invasion with the help of a nerdy scientist and a struggling female rock singer.

title: Snake Eyes
description: A G.I. Joe spin-off centered around the character of Snake Eyes.

description: The young warrior Son Goku sets out on a quest, racing against time and the vengeful King Piccolo, to collect a set of seven magical orbs that will grant their wielder unlimited power.

description: As the threat of giant unidentified lifeforms known as "S-Class Species" worsens in Japan, a silver giant appears from beyond Earth's atmosphere.

title: Bloodshot
description: Ray Garrison, a slain soldier, is re-animated with superpowers.

description: When the world's best spy is turned into a pigeon, he must rely on his nerdy tech officer to save the world.

description: It's been five years since everything was awesome and the citizens are facing a huge new threat: Lego Duplo invaders from outer space, wrecking everything faster than they can rebuild.

title: Spawn

title: Wonder Woman 3
description: Plot unknown. Third installment of the 'Wonder Woman' franchise.

description: When the world is threatened by an ancient evil, the four adolescent turtles must reunite and overcome their faults in order to stand against it.

description: When Frank Castle's family is murdered by criminals, he wages war on crime as a vigilante assassin known only as The Punisher.

description: When dosed with cosmic rays, four intrepid explorers are given incredible powers.

description: Ladybug & Cat Noir Awakening, is an upcoming animated musical film based on Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir. It will be released in Fall 2021, or Early 2022.

title: Monster Family 2
description: To free Baba Yaga and Renfield from the clutches of Monster Hunter Mila Starr, the Wishbone Family once more transforms into a Vampire, Frankenstein's Monster, a Mummy and a Werewolf. Aided and abetted by their three pet bats, our Monster Family zooms around the world again to save their friends, make new monstrous acquaintances and finally come to the realization tha...

title: Spider-Man: Beyond the Spider-Verse
description: After leaving off from Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse, the story continues.

title: Red Sonja
description: Plot kept under wraps. An adaptation of the comic book, Red Sonja, a vengeful warrior known as a "She-Devil with a sword".
